    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《合成大猫咪》是一款轻松上手、超级上头的动物合成游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐱合成相同的小动物，就能获得分数！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐶合成更多动物，分数也会随之上涨！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆与全球玩家同台竞技，不断合成、冲击高分，赢得奖杯！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/02cc58a4fbac9eeaa92a6998b6a73c3b.avif?t=1772095922\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的玩法非常简单，拖动并发射小动物，让它们“砰”地碰撞，就能进行合成。两只大鹅会合成为大猫咪、两只大猫咪会合成为大狗，随着合成的次数增多，分数也在飙升，根本停不下来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/316c1baeb2b2cbdc6c4f888fce5f144a.poster.avif?t=1772095922\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/316c1baeb2b2cbdc6c4f888fce5f144a.webm?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/316c1baeb2b2cbdc6c4f888fce5f144a.mp4?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/438af6d2546b776f7b387f9be6448dfa.avif?t=1772095922\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次合成都有机会打破以往纪录，与全世界的玩家实时比拼！参加每周、每月的比赛，冲击排行榜顶端，解锁更多奖杯，成为真正的合成大师！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d211f2b24a582b5e84d865661beb28d7.poster.avif?t=1772095922\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d211f2b24a582b5e84d865661beb28d7.webm?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d211f2b24a582b5e84d865661beb28d7.mp4?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/ad1738b063b50f7d7bb1bce983f3b7c9.avif?t=1772095922\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动物的落点会影响整体布局，合成还会推动周围动物，稍有不慎就会越界失败！留足空间、掌握节奏，才是合成高手的不二法门！只有精打细算、排兵布阵，才能笑到最后！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d7bad7cae946c2d67f7f884fedb7c205.poster.avif?t=1772095922\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d7bad7cae946c2d67f7f884fedb7c205.webm?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181470/extras/d7bad7cae946c2d67f7f884fedb7c205.mp4?t=1772095922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
